@startuml UEORMS_State_12_Single
top to bottom direction
hide empty description
title UEORMS State Transition - Module 12

[*] --> Startup
Startup --> Healthy : checks pass
Startup --> Degraded : checks fail

Healthy --> AccessCheck : request arrives
AccessCheck --> Processed : pass auth/rbac/limit
AccessCheck --> SecurityEvent : denied or throttled

Processed --> Healthy : normal metrics
Processed --> Degraded : incident detected

Degraded --> Recovering : auto recovery
Recovering --> Healthy : recovered
Recovering --> ManualFix : auto recovery failed
ManualFix --> Healthy : operator fixed

SecurityEvent --> Healthy : event logged
Healthy --> [*] : maintenance shutdown

@enduml
